## FILE DEPENDENCY GRAPH

```
Users' Machines
    â”‚
    â”œâ”€ Execute: launch_setup.bat
    â”‚   â”‚
    â”‚   â””â”€â†’ first_run_setup.pyw (GUI)
    â”‚       â”‚
    â”‚       â””â”€â†’ setup_wizard.py (Backend)
    â”‚           â”‚
    â”‚           â”œâ”€â†’ config.yaml (Generated)
    â”‚           â””â”€â†’ (reads config_schema)
    â”‚
    â””â”€ Later: launch_assistant_gui.pyw
        â”‚
        â””â”€â†’ gui_assistant.py
            â”‚
            â””â”€â†’ assistant_core.py
                â”‚
                â””â”€â†’ config.yaml (Generated by setup)
```

**So apply patches in this order:**
1. config.yaml (structure)
2. assistant_core.py (uses config)
3. setup_wizard.py (creates config)
4. first_run_setup.pyw (GUI for setup_wizard.py)

